{"tid":2408141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德甲球會拜仁慕尼黑用青天白日旗向中国球迷拜年","createTime":"2021-02-14T15:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T17:07:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cc124c431f9f2c4b4a7ddb9fd06bf785ffb346e0","tid":2408141,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/gm-flag-02142021093854.html/@@images/88a43ac4-66d8-4f33-a988-431b829a7995.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fgm-flag-02142021093854.html%2F%40%40images%2F88a43ac4-66d8-4f33-a988-431b829a7995.jpeg&h=5e289edc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德甲球會拜仁慕尼黑官方Facebook一篇向大陸球迷拜年的帖文，因誤用台灣旗幟，被大陸網民猛烈抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n德國甲組足球聯賽班霸拜仁慕尼黑於上周五（12日）年初一當天，在Facebook以多國語言向亞洲不同地區的華人球迷拜年，但在一篇以簡體字寫上「新年快樂」的貼文中，卻配上青天白日滿地紅旗，引起大陸球迷不滿。球會翌日下午回覆大陸媒體稱，已立即意識到這是一個非常嚴重且不可接受的錯誤，並第一時間刪除發文。<br />\n<br />\n球會稱Facebook帳號是由第三方公司負責運作，球會在確定賀年的海報照片後，由該公司負責發布文字。但由於第三方公司失誤，導致向大陸球迷拜年時用錯了旗幟。球會周日（14日）亦在官方微博帳戶發聲明表示，對很多人因此事在情感上受到了傷害深表歉意，強調一直以來球會都非常重視大陸與德國文化交流，對於此次犯下的錯誤，會認真總結，嚴肅處理，並在今後的工作中引以為戒。<br />\n<br />\n這次已非該球會首次在社交網發文引發爭議。2019年年底，球會為答謝兩岸球迷支持，分別以五星旗和青天白日旗製作照片上傳Facebook。惟相關發文事後均被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/gm-flag-02142021093854.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fgm-flag-02142021093854.html&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=1ef257d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/gm-flag-02142021093854.html</a>"},{"pid":"8e291e1487d95d317218fbcd4081b6da4569d0fd","tid":2408141,"uid":16465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"拜仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1a29f386197995b1a4730ebc3748efa1d435ba","tid":2408141,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e291e1487d95d317218fbcd4081b6da4569d0fd","tid":2408141,"uid":16465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"拜仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:08:17.000Z","msg":"跪了"},{"pid":"afcb957a48d5fb3ccc279ac844e489ef80c639b2","tid":2408141,"uid":300023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEnGb6m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEnGb6m.jpg&h=9daafd57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f848d7b3044b84822334eb93a8ca2c9703be2c3","tid":2408141,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"用簡體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8beb24ea7365c06137007901d03d33ae3e383992","tid":2408141,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:14:41.000Z","msg":"奶共奶得咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6700d481efa7e5dedbe1320229a3d9cc96738c","tid":2408141,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9b2704702f25bd8499866bc76396af8c2d23a6","tid":2408141,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"抵屌 殘体字丫嗱"},{"pid":"9f2049fd16861f7a16b6f84fa5c7ee7c6ac2c79f","tid":2408141,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8beb24ea7365c06137007901d03d33ae3e383992","tid":2408141,"uid":3451